@startuml 15-state-vessel-call
title State Machine — Vessel Call Lifecycle

[*] --> Scheduled : vessel call created

Scheduled --> Approaching : AIS ETA within\n24h threshold
Scheduled --> Cancelled : voyage cancelled

Approaching --> Berthed : ATA recorded\nberth allocated
Approaching --> Scheduled : ETA revised\n(outside window)

Berthed --> Departed : ATD recorded\nall cargo handled
Berthed --> Approaching : emergency departure\n(re-berthing)

Departed --> [*]

Cancelled --> [*]

note right of Approaching
  Kafka: vessel.arrivals
  Agent: vessel-agent
  ML: vessel-delay-prediction
end note

note right of Berthed
  Kafka: berth.allocations
  Agent: container-agent
  MCP: tos-mcp
end note

@enduml
